reviews.text:
Quite impress with zhi char called Gim Seng Seafood at Tam Chiak Bidadari Kopitiam.
We have been ordering their curry fish head every time we patronize their stall.
Food taste and quality always consistent so far.
Prices are fair and service is good & friendly
Recommended.

Been here 3 times. Love the foods & environment, it is airy & staffs also very friendly. Serving quite fast also.

Gim Seng Seafood never disappoints. I‚Äôve ordered from them multiple times and also dined in on several occasions. The food is consistently flavorful, well-prepared, and fresh. Service is attentive and efficient, making every visit a great experience. Definitely a go-to spot for quality seafood and excellent service. Highly recommended!

Overall food was mediocre. Their signature lotus leaf steamed chicken dish was tasteless and cold.
Dining experience felt rushed as the staff placed the next reservation's placard on the table and started clearing our dishes while we were still eating.
For a group of ~10pax, we were only given ~1hr 15min to eat although we made a reservation.
